{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "21", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "22", "M": "56", "S": "29"}}, "news": [{"title": "Prestige Estates Projects' net profit rises 111.61% to \u20b91,305.4 crore in FY26", "para": "Prestige Estates Projects reported a significant 111.61% surge in its net consolidated profit for FY26, reaching \u20b91,305.4 crore. The company's total income also saw a substantial increase of 70.58% to \u20b913,195.5 crore.  The board recommended a 20% final dividend and approved a \u20b92,000 crore non-convertible debenture issuance.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/prestige-estates-projects-reports-11161-surge-in-net-profit-for-fy26/131250290?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-24738/131250290.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "MHADA reviews progress of housing projects in Kalyan taluka", "para": "MHADA vice-president and CEO Sanjeev Jaiswal reviewed the progress of housing projects being developed by the Konkan Housing and Area Development Board at Khoni, Shirdhon, Gotheghar and Bhandarli in Thane district. The projects include large-scale housing for economically weaker and low-income groups, along with shops and civic amenities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/mhada-accelerates-housing-development-in-kalyan-taluka/131248232?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-84250/131248232.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "MHADA starts allotment of 827 rehab units in Worli BDD Chawl redevelopment project", "para": "MHADA has started issuing allotment letters and possession of rehabilitation tenements in the first rehab building of the Worli BDD Chawl redevelopment project. On the first day, 41 eligible residents were issued allotment letters and